better than any of us.

888
00:56:10,240 --> 00:56:11,195
Sam...

889
00:56:11,480 --> 00:56:12,754
Say a few words?

890
00:56:18,280 --> 00:56:21,238
Well, you folks who remember my father...

891
00:56:21,640 --> 00:56:23,392
...knew him as sheriff.

892
00:56:23,960 --> 00:56:27,077
But at home he was also judge, jury...

893
00:56:28,520 --> 00:56:29,919
...and executioner.

894
00:56:32,480 --> 00:56:35,119
