905
00:57:35,480 --> 00:57:38,199
I think he'll run that Mexican kid in
for loitering.

906
00:57:38,280 --> 00:57:40,191
Nice to see you, Mrs. Cruz.

907
00:57:51,200 --> 00:57:52,633
Field trip?

908
